The paper discusses the challenges and requirements in developing benchmarks for big data systems, which involves capturing, storing, managing, analyzing, and visualizing big data. This aligns with the topics covered in the databases (cs.DB), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-categories.
